Found a bug or have a suggestion?  
👉 Open an issue here: **[github.com/freheCode/freheSwipe/issues](https://github.com/freheCode/freheSwipe/issues)**

Please include:  
- Browser + version  
- Steps to reproduce  
- Expected vs actual behavior  

